<P>
CHANGING THE ENDANGERED SPECIES ACT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In reading the remarks of Fein and Meese I did not know whether to laugh or 
cry. My God, they're serious! 
</P>
<P>
