<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA080990-0040 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 259042 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 9, 1990, Thursday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 7; Column 2; Op-Ed Desk 
