for the first nine months totaled $234,000, down from $478,000 last year. The 
fiscal 1989 nine months' revenue included a pretax charge to operations of $1.1 
million from the write-down of assets as well as a gain of $748,000 from an 
accounting change. Sales for the first three quarters declined 10%, to $9.2 
million from $10.2 million. 
