ARMED FORCES -- SAUDI ARABIA; CHEMICAL WARFARE; CHEMICAL WEAPONS -- IRAQ; 
UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- IRAQ; POISONS AND POISONINGS; NERVE GAS; 
MILITARY EQUIPMENT AND SUPPLIES; MILITARY AIRPLANES; PERSIAN GULF 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
