Independence battle group: 
</P>
<P>
Forrestal-class aircraft carrier: Independence 
</P>
<P>
Guided-missile cruiser: Jouett 
</P>
<P>
Guided-missile destroyer: Goldsborough 
</P>
<P>
Frigates: Brewton and Reasoner 
</P>
<P>
Supply ships: Cimarron and Flint 
</P>
