<P>
COLLEGE NEWS: USC SCIENTIST WINS SWISS ACADEMY PRIZE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Franz Hefti of Altadena, a neuroscientist at USC's Leonard Davis School of 
Gerontology, has been awarded the $30,000 Robert Bing Prize by the Swiss 
Academy of Medical Sciences. 
</P>
