<P>
NEIGHBORHOOD EATERY: MORE EATERIES: 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By M. FLAGG 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Villa Margarita, 103 Santa Isabel Ave., Costa Mesa. Open daily 4 p.m. to 
midnight; weekends till 2 a.m. (714) 631-6602. 
</P>
<P>
This is the sort of place you want to take three or four friends, scarf up some 
excellent nachos and drink some very reasonably priced and 
generous-on-the-good-stuff margaritas. The place is a dump, but a nice dump. A 
homey dump. M. FLAGG 
</P>
