MILITARY CONFRONTATIONS; IRAQ -- ARMED FORCES -- KUWAIT; IRAQ -- FOREIGN 
RELATIONS -- KUWAIT; IRAQ -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- SAUDI ARABIA; EMERGENCY 
PREPAREDNESS; EVACUATIONS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
