<P>
Recall attempt -- A story in the Aug. 2 edition of The Times incorrectly stated 
that organizers of a recall attempt against two trustees in the Inglewood 
Unified School District had withdrawn their effort. The story should have said 
that the organizers of the recall did not submit the required signatures to the 
county registrar-recorder's office by the July 17 deadline. 
</P>
