<P>
Sara Lee Corp. said today its profit rose 15.3% in its fourth fiscal quarter, 
despite a decline in revenue and lower results from its packaged meats and 
bakery products businesses. 
</P>
<P>
The packaged food and consumer products company said it earned $118.4 million, 
or 48 cents per share, in the three months ended June 30 compared with $102.7 
