<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Seniors feature -- The Seniors feature in the June 21 edition of Ventura County 
Life gave the incorrect name for the son of Luisa Hyun. He is in fact Michael 
Losey, also son of director Joseph Losey. 
</P>
